  <summary date="2022-03-17T14:21:19Z" status="Passed Senate">Sunshine Protection Act of 2021

This bill makes daylight saving time the new, permanent standard time, effective November 5, 2023.

States with areas exempt from daylight saving time may choose the standard time for those areas.</summary>
